  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "This magical shield is imbued with properties befitting a worshipper of Torm, and its use is limited to those of lawful good alignment.\n\nTorm the True and the Brave is the god of duty loyalty, and obedience, and the patron of paladins and those who face danger for a greater good.\n\nTorm's symbol is a metal gauntlet. Torm's is one of the most ethically pure of all faiths, in that it is devoted to loyalty and obedience.  He benefits from an enthusiastic following, and number of fighting orders and paladins have devoted themselves to this god."
    }
